      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><thought\n>It's not just \"tough days\" though. It feels like every time I try to fix things, I just make it worse for them. I look at them and I just see how much my mess is affecting their lives. It's like I'm a constant weight on their shoulders. I can't shake the feeling that if I wasn't around, they'd actually have a chance to be happy and stable. They'd finally be free from all this.",
